bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was reported to the House on November 12, 2014. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Designates the segment of Interstate Route 35 between milepost 133 at Forest Lake, Minnesota, and milepost 259 at Duluth, Minnesota, as the "James L. Oberstar Memorial Highway."
